name: HD-08
description:
Enjoy all your favorite butters and oils in one fun jar! This fluffy cream is great for nourishing the scalp, sealing ends, setting styles, and adding shine!

Ingredients: Shea butter, Jojoba Oil, Black Jamaican Castor Oil, Sweet Almond Oil, Peach Oil, Lemongrass Oil, Aloe Vera Juice, Seaweed Extract
